thread.title: Keziah Jeftha
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Keziah Jeftha

author: Keziah Jeftha
title: Keziah Jeftha
text: Had no problem with collecting beautiful new car and got our journey started without a problem. Missed not having a manual to assist with familiarising us with this new vehicle but not big issue. We needed to replace booster seat with child car seat and we had great assistance getting that sorted. On return of vehicle there was issue with us not having the 'checklist' which must have gone astray. The matter was dealt with so professionally that it was sorted in no time and no delay with our departure. We have been very impressed with the service. Good work Omega!
